SIGN 0 0
  Info Guy:
"So you wanna know about
the sailor rock pile eh? Well
I'll tell ya about it!

  One day, about thirty-five
years ago, a group of pirates
came to steal our food supply.
A brave group of sailors manag-
ed to halt the pirate attack by
taunting them with dead fish.
After the pirates fled in terror,
the sailors also left, but before
they did, they make a pile of
rocks, probably to remind us
of how they saved us or some-
thing"
SIGNEND
SIGN 0 0
  Info Guy:
"So you wanna know about
the town well eh? Well
I'll tell ya about it!

  One day, a long time ago, the
very first mayor of Nimda was
out for a walk, and he became
thirsty. He eventually stumbled
across a waterhole and drank
some water. 
  From that day on, that waterhole
is the town well"
SIGNEND
SIGN 0 0
  Info Guy:
"So you wanna know about
the Nimda timber mill eh? Well
I'll tell ya about it!

  One night  years ago during a 
terrible storm the Nimba Lumber 
Company was working overtime 
producing timber from 
its mill. The rain was pouring 
down and the captain didnt 
want to risk lossing the load, 
but the owner of the mill 
disagreed and force the issue. 
Mintues after the boat set off it 
ran aground on a sandbar."
SIGNEND
SIGN 0 0
  Info Guy:
"So you wanna know about
the old sunken ship eh? Well
I'll tell ya about it!

  It turns out, that the ship is the
remains of an old timber boat
that sank during a storm. Some
say it's haunted, others say it
smells like dead fish. Who
knows!"
SIGNEND
