  The prime source of all things
is wood in Nimda. Home to many
forests animals. It's said that
a dragon used to have a castle
set up deep in the forest where
he'd guide a very
valuable treasure"
SIGNEND
SIGN 0 0
  Info Guy:
"So you wanna know about
the Ninja Castle eh? 
Well I'll tell ya about it!

 Long time ago Master Li of
the Ninjas founded a castle
in the west of Nimda where
he studied the ancient Ninja
art of poisoning weapons.
Deep did he make the halls
of his castle and he tried to
get more room by going even
deeper when he hit a cave of
trolls. Little do we know about
this creatures except that they
are nearly impossible to defeat.
They had to run and to stop
Nimda from being conquered
by trolls he sealed the door.
